name: 3 Bedroom Duplex
about:
Introducing a stunning duplex nestled within the tranquil Mangrove Estate, Lagos State, Nigeria. This spacious abode boasts three bedrooms, each accompanied by its own private bathroom, offering unparalleled comfort and convenience. With a generous 2000 square feet of living space, there's ample room for relaxation and entertaining alike. 
Noteworthy features include two dedicated parking spaces, ensuring hassle-free accommodation for your vehicles. Step inside to discover a meticulously designed interior, where modern aesthetics blend seamlessly with practicality. The open-plan layout creates an inviting atmosphere, perfect for hosting gatherings or simply unwinding after a long day.
